WEBVTT

00:10.069 --> 00:12.196
Hey, Senor McKay.
Que pasa, bud?

00:12.237 --> 00:13.363
Hey, brother, what's up?

00:13.405 --> 00:15.566
l just got done
stuffing my face.

00:15.607 --> 00:17.871
Cool, l just got done
taking my last final.

00:17.910 --> 00:19.571
l'm a free man till
next semester starts.

00:19.611 --> 00:21.010
Yeah, what are you going
to do with all that freedom?

00:21.080 --> 00:22.411
Probably nothing.

00:22.448 --> 00:23.710
That's a novel concept.

00:23.749 --> 00:25.239
Well, l had two trips planned,

00:25.284 --> 00:27.479
but then with the Peach Pit
After Dark opening this week,

00:27.519 --> 00:28.543
Donna canceled our annual

00:28.587 --> 00:29.554
ski trip to Arrowhead,

00:29.588 --> 00:30.987
and then Kelly and l were going

00:31.023 --> 00:32.991
to Palm Springs,
but with the burn,

00:33.025 --> 00:35.220
she doesn't want to be laying
by the pool, getting a tan.

00:35.260 --> 00:36.420
Yeah, yeah,
so what do you think,

00:36.462 --> 00:38.157
you want to take
a little road trip with me?

00:38.197 --> 00:39.255
What'd you have in mind?

00:39.298 --> 00:40.663
l was thinking
maybe Lake Whitney,

00:40.699 --> 00:41.825
couple of days, camping out.

00:41.867 --> 00:43.334
Cool. When do we leave?

00:43.368 --> 00:44.335
ln about an hour.

00:44.369 --> 00:45.461
No, seriously,
when do we leave?

00:45.504 --> 00:47.199
ln about an hour.
l only got three days

00:47.239 --> 00:48.866
and my probation kicks in,
l lose my driver's license.

00:48.907 --> 00:50.499
So, that's cool. l'll drive.

00:50.542 --> 00:53.238
No, dude, when l said road trip,
l was thinking of a...

00:53.278 --> 00:55.109
road trip.

00:56.582 --> 00:58.573
You want to go to Lake Whitney
on motorcycles?!

00:58.617 --> 01:01.177
The thought had crossed my mind.

01:03.000 --> 01:09.074
